First off,<br>
<br>
Did you all read what Aradune posted on the Sony boards? He said some fairly big changes are coming down the road for EQ.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/everquest/Forum2/HTML/045774.html">boards.station.sony.com/e...45774.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
He talks about re-doing some of the old world dungeons in order to get more people in them. He didnt want to make them high level dungeons per say but change their pathing, and make them more like &quot;kunark or Velious&quot; dungeons whatever that means? IMO that may mean redefining loot tables and etc. He also stated something about putting bind points in front of these older dungeons as well. Would be nice to be a 22nd level warrior and be able to bind right outfront Unrest for example.<br>
<br>
He also talked about significantly increasing the group XP bonus. Real cool IMO. It would help counter some grouping problems. I'm all for jacking up the group XP bonus. Also he was saying they would be doing it per member, so it makes sense to round out to a full 6 members now. <br>
<br>
Further on he mentioned about tossing in some new quests, etc etc etc. All in all some good news from VI.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Secondly,<br>
<br>
I have been reading some player pleas on Verant's board about people being banned for duping. Seems VI is on the crackdown move for dupers. Good, dupers suck. However after reading some things im a bit confused and perplexed. Some people are saying they were banned simply because they unknowingly had a duped item in their posession. This is something that I have heard about before, and it bothers me. What if I, in a legitimate trade in EC unknowingly traded for an item that had been duped 3 players back? Would I be &quot;busted&quot; for duping? I dont dupe, never have duped, or even knew anyone who duped....but it seems a legit player could get an item in trade that had been unknowingly duped by a player several trades back and when they crack down on duping you could get busted too? Is this right? This seems to be the messsage im getting from their boards....?<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
</font><P>Belegir Swiftbow,
just a Ranger



